{"tid":1403152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Weekday 升級支援方案 『和理非』都可輕鬆參與！（續）","createTime":"2019-08-03T17:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:34:19.000Z","uid":36432,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"856e437f6abc541d42131a95e07dba5e419d2ae8","tid":1403152,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:54:15.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係上個Post嘅樓主朋友<br />\n<br />\n原文Link：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1391869/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1391869/</a><br />\n<br />\n今次開Post係講下黎緊星期四，行街食野有咩攻略，如果TLDR嘅，不妨Follow返 @trybeforeyoubuy， 拎住最新資訊❤️做個精明消費者。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eir685U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEir685U.jpg&h=1328d935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抱住「開心個人遊商場」出去時，以下係一啲參考資料。<br />\n<br />\n要黑衫，口罩？<br />\n一個個人，自發嘅行動，無須Dress Code同口號。不過空氣唔好戴個口罩都好合理🤡。<br />\n<br />\n點解行海港城？<br />\n除咗交通方便，有船/巴/地鐵外，海港城亦有種類繁多嘅店舖，滿足晒每個人嘅需要。更重要一點，係海港城有好多內地旅客，自發行街嘅你，要多啲同遊客溝通哦。<br />\n<br />\n會犯法嗎？<br />\n行商場絕對冇犯法，幫商場增加人流出師有名。慢慢行慢慢睇，又唔會造成財物損失，做個精明嘅消/不消費者。<br />\n<br />\n行街有咩用？<br />\n商場人多好，但人太多，你應接不暇就商家自己諗方法解決了，如果商家因為做生意上有困難，向政府表達，因而取消某啲極具爭議性同影響力嘅政策，我都感到&hellip;好難過哦😗。<br />\n<br />\n咁大個商場行邊好先？<br />\n以下Google Link，有星級推薦名單俾大家😀，自發活動，大家去邊都得架👍。提一提，千祈唔好三四個人喺商戶門口堵路，因為咁樣人哋就做唔到生意，記住，&quot;千祈千祈唔好&quot;塞住個門囗呀。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家星期四可以行得開心，玩得放心啦。🥳<br />\n<br />\n🔥五大訴求 缺一不可🔥<br />\n✨光復香港 時代革命✨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtK1dxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmtK1dxv.jpg&h=4589874a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a7e6c36d2d24c9aa32a2f9ea2fb6b83bc88cf63","tid":1403152,"uid":36432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:54:43.000Z","msg":"推呢個！！！"},{"pid":"ef1b9608fccf37a0fca60e03b155909081f5433b","tid":1403152,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:54:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fe643e7665166f26574108498f4b7e3e5b92b6f5","tid":1403152,"uid":99499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:58:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80341ee7dbdd7b732d23f2517d8ceaa5aa6a1f7e","tid":1403152,"uid":189961,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:58:48.000Z","msg":"推 逐個商場咁慢慢擊破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fecc81bcc192d5b34849767c044488dc7004b5","tid":1403152,"uid":36432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fe643e7665166f26574108498f4b7e3e5b92b6f5","tid":1403152,"uid":99499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:58:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:01:10.000Z","msg":"sorry sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />8號現場慢慢屌我"},{"pid":"af8000ee76eb39539baecd61429321cab705d363","tid":1403152,"uid":99499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:10:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7746d3a533a2da35f6aab8bd0f80f3ec47b23145","tid":1403152,"uid":99499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:11:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ede72c4a8979861f5e5765d752f3f938b9688d35","tid":1403152,"uid":99499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:12:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"415b2b4d90e48b49245a284a358db512b67c2548","tid":1403152,"uid":99499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:14:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e19740dda8e89d921f8df70510de3d267b7bda03","tid":1403152,"uid